reviewText: I like this collection of the Scorpion King.  I just wish it had all three movie, then I would have rated it higher.

I orederd the set of the Scorpion king.  It was a good price and was shipped promptly.  Once we opened it the 2nd movie's disc was missing.  I contacted the seller and they immediately credited me for the whole purchase because they could not find the 2nd disc in their location.  I was very pleased with how they handled the situation.  I would purchase from them again!
